  "content": "eats raw compute for small models.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">If data transfer costs more than the computation, zero-copy wins.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128736;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px;\">Don't discard your iGPU.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">It's free compute sitting idle. For embeddings, it can match or beat a discrete GPU.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128268;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px;\">Make backend switching painless.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Different hardware, different optimal backends. Let users switch at runtime.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 40px 0 28px;\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 14px;\">\n      Running embedding inference locally?<br>What backends have worked best for you?\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">\n      Full benchmark report + reproduction steps on GitHub &#128071;\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">08 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
